Package: PDcalc
Title: An implementation of the Phylogenetic Diversity (PD) calculus in R
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R: c(person("David", "Nipperess", email = "david.nipperess@mq.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
          person("Peter", "Wilson", email = "peter.wilson@mq.edu.au", role = "aut"))
Description: PDcalc is a package for calculating various diversity
    measures based on Phylogenetic Diversity. This measurement
    framework is referred to by Dan Faith as the "PD calculus".
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports:
    ape
